body: I give the story a 9/10, great story but I'm not a fan of Futa without any balls, Still a great story and a big Plot twist at the end 😂

Fap wise? 8/10
Story wise? 6/10
came for the fap stayed for the plot

And shit, the decapitation was a great plot twist. Honestly, could've ended there, with the tentaculus dying (I appreciate the scenes after tho lmao). If sword has no effect, wtf do they use it for then? Damn it author I thought this was gonna be a story beyond simple hentai.

For a fap it's good but the story could use some better writing. For example, the tentaculus was broken af, infinite growth rate out of nowhere. I mean, they held off fine till the start of the story, then they get overwhelmed? Wtf? And apparently for no reason. Supposedly they were elite, elite at what? Getting fucked? Maybe I'm kinda rambling cause of the anticlimatic ending, but I was expecting more. Beyond the hot fappable material, I kinda got invested on the plot. Like the tentacle took over the world, now what? How tf do they get fed now? Nvm, good shit, 8/10,would've liked a better turn of events.

Man, I was hoping for a different ending. If she was going to give in like that, I don't really see why it had to be so long. Maybe if there was a compromise or something, like being the bride in exchange for leaving the rest of humanity alone, but nah, it was just fall into pleasure like she should've in the first chapter.
